panels.title: Overview (updates based on top time selection)

targets.rawSQL:
SELECT $__unixEpochGroup(time / 1000, '${interval}') as time, type, client_ip, target_group_arn, target_ip, elb_status_code_group, elb_status_code, request_verb, request_host, request_path, ssl_protocol, ua_os, ua_device, ua_browser, ua_category, geo_iso_code, geo_country, geo_city
	, sum(received_bytes) as received_bytes, sum(sent_bytes) as sent_bytes, sum(request_processing_time) as request_processing_time, sum(target_processing_time) as target_processing_time, sum(response_processing_time) as response_processing_time, sum(requests) as requests
FROM "$__table"
WHERE elb IN (${elb:sqlstring}) 
	AND type IN (${type:sqlstring}) 
	AND elb_status_code_group IN (${elb_status_code_group:sqlstring}) 
	AND target_group_arn IN (${target_group_arn:sqlstring}) 
	AND request_verb IN (${http_method:sqlstring})
	AND $__unixEpochFilter(time / 1000)
  AND (event_hour BETWEEN  $__rawTimeFrom('yyyyMMddHH') AND  $__rawTimeTo('yyyyMMddHH')
	OR event_hour = $__rawTimeFrom('yyyyMMdd00'))
GROUP BY $__unixEpochGroup(time / 1000, '${interval}'), type, client_ip, target_group_arn, target_ip, elb_status_code_group, elb_status_code, request_verb, request_host, request_path, ssl_protocol, ua_os, ua_device, ua_browser, ua_category, geo_iso_code, geo_country, geo_city
